### Common Command Patterns

```bash
# Next.js / React projects
npm run dev          # Start dev server (localhost:3000)
npm run build        # Production build
npm run start        # Start production server
npm run lint         # ESLint check
npm run test         # Run Vitest/Jest tests
npm run test:watch   # Tests in watch mode
npm run typecheck    # tsc --noEmit

# Node.js API projects
npm run dev          # nodemon or tsx watch
npm run build        # tsc or esbuild
npm run start        # node dist/index.js
npm run test         # vitest or jest
npm run db:migrate   # Run database migrations
npm run db:seed      # Seed development data

# Monorepo (Turborepo)
npm run dev          # turbo run dev
npm run build        # turbo run build
npm run test         # turbo run test
```

## Custom Slash Commands

- `/dev-docs [task]` - Create strategic implementation plan
- `/dev-docs-update` - Update plan before context compaction
- `/build-and-fix` - Run build and fix all errors
- `/code-review` - Architecture review against best practices
- `/test-api [endpoint]` - Test API endpoints

